  <http://www.ebu.ch/metadata/ontologies/ebucore/ebucore#hasAgentBiography> "Based in Kjipuktuk/Halifax, Live Art Dance is a hub of the arts on the East Coast. We programme local, national, and international work, offering our artists and audiences a diverse and rich season of contemporary dance. Our presentations are accompanied by deep and carefully considered outreach, programmed with an eye to increasing engagement with artistic voices, building connections, and celebrating the diversity of artistic practice."@en,
